                <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;\n%%{init: {\n  \&quot;theme\&quot;: \&quot;base\&quot;,\n  \&quot;themeVariables\&quot;: {\n    \&quot;background\&quot;: \&quot;#ffffff\&quot;,\n    \&quot;primaryColor\&quot;: \&quot;#ffffff\&quot;,\n    \&quot;primaryBorderColor\&quot;: \&quot;#334155\&quot;,\n    \&quot;primaryTextColor\&quot;: \&quot;#111827\&quot;,\n    \&quot;actorBkg\&quot;: \&quot;#ffffff\&quot;,\n    \&quot;actorBorder\&quot;: \&quot;#334155\&quot;,\n    \&quot;actorTextColor\&quot;: \&quot;#111827\&quot;,\n    \&quot;lineColor\&quot;: \&quot;#334155\&quot;,\n    \&quot;signalColor\&quot;: \&quot;#334155\&quot;,\n    \&quot;signalTextColor\&quot;: \&quot;#111827\&quot;,\n    \&quot;activationBkgColor\&quot;: \&quot;#f8fafc\&quot;,\n    \&quot;activationBorderColor\&quot;: \&quot;#64748b\&quot;,\n    \&quot;sequenceNumberColor\&quot;: \&quot;#111827\&quot;\n  }\n}}%%\n\nsequenceDiagram\n    autonumber\n\n    actor User as Người dùng\n    participant FE as Frontend\n    participant API as Backend API\n    participant Scan as Menu Scan Module\n    participant Auth as Identity Module\n    participant Rec as Recommend Module\n    participant RAG as RAG Engine\n    participant VDB as Vector DB\n    participant LLM as LLM\n    participant Storage as Object Storage\n    participant DB as Database\n\n    rect rgb(239, 246, 255)\n        User-&gt;&gt;FE: Upload ảnh menu + chọn ngôn ngữ\n        FE-&gt;&gt;API: POST /menu-scans {image, target_language, token?}\n        API-&gt;&gt;Scan: scanMenu(image, target_language, token?)\n    end\n\n    rect rgb(248, 250, 252)\n        Scan-&gt;&gt;Storage: Lưu ảnh menu\n        Storage--&gt;&gt;Scan: image_url\n        Scan-&gt;&gt;Auth: Kiểm tra token\n        Auth--&gt;&gt;Scan: user_id hoặc anonymous\n    end\n\n    alt Đã đăng nhập\n        rect rgb(220, 252, 231)\n            Scan-&gt;&gt;Rec: Lấy hồ sơ ăn uống\n            Rec-&gt;&gt;DB: Query user food profile\n            DB--&gt;&gt;Rec: preferences / allergies / disliked foods\n            Rec--&gt;&gt;Scan: user_preferences\n        end\n\n        rect rgb(224, 242, 254)\n            Scan-&gt;&gt;RAG: Lấy context theo menu + user_preferences\n            RAG-&gt;&gt;VDB: Similarity search\n            VDB--&gt;&gt;RAG: relevant context\n            RAG--&gt;&gt;Scan: context\n        end\n\n        rect rgb(240, 253, 244)\n            Scan-&gt;&gt;LLM: Scan menu + dịch + cá nhân hóa\n            LLM--&gt;&gt;Scan: menu_items + recommendations\n            Scan-&gt;&gt;DB: Lưu lịch sử scan + kết quả\n            DB--&gt;&gt;Scan: Lưu thành công\n            Scan--&gt;&gt;API: Kết quả cá nhân hóa\n            API--&gt;&gt;FE: 200 OK + menu_items\n            FE--&gt;&gt;User: Hiển thị menu đã dịch + gợi ý\n        end\n\n    else Chưa đăng nhập\n        rect rgb(224, 242, 254)\n            Scan-&gt;&gt;RAG: Lấy context theo menu + ngôn ngữ\n            RAG-&gt;&gt;VDB: Similarity search\n            VDB--&gt;&gt;RAG: relevant context\n            RAG--&gt;&gt;Scan: context\n        end\n\n        rect rgb(240, 253, 244)\n            Scan-&gt;&gt;LLM: Scan menu + dịch\n            LLM--&gt;&gt;Scan: menu_items\n            Scan--&gt;&gt;API: Kết quả cơ bản\n            API--&gt;&gt;FE: 200 OK + menu_items\n            FE--&gt;&gt;User: Hiển thị menu đã dịch\n        end\n\n        rect rgb(254, 249, 195)\n            Note over Scan,Storage: Chỉ lưu ảnh vào Object Storage\n            Note over Scan,DB: Không lưu lịch sử / thông tin user\n        end\n    end&quot;&#xa;}" id="2">
